Kopírovanie po megabajtových blokoch funguje výborne, s takou istou metodou ako kopírovanie znak po znaku, len namiesto 1 bajt som používal 1024.
(content infile-u som vymazal, lebo som to otestoval s 5MB súborom)

patrick@DESKTOP-I4LLMQU:/mnt/c/Users/patri/Documents/OS/OS-domace/T02/os2022-sr0910-usr/T02/07$ ls -l infile
-rwxrwxrwx 1 patrick patrick 5242880 Oct  7 02:47 infile

patrick@DESKTOP-I4LLMQU:/mnt/c/Users/patri/Documents/OS/OS-domace/T02/os2022-sr0910-usr/T02/07$ ls -l outfile
-rwxrwxrwx 1 patrick patrick 0 Oct  7 02:53 outfile

patrick@DESKTOP-I4LLMQU:/mnt/c/Users/patri/Documents/OS/OS-domace/T02/os2022-sr0910-usr/T02/07$ ./07 <infile >outfile

patrick@DESKTOP-I4LLMQU:/mnt/c/Users/patri/Documents/OS/OS-domace/T02/os2022-sr0910-usr/T02/07$ ls -l outfile
-rwxrwxrwx 1 patrick patrick 5242911 Oct  7 02:56 outfile
